{"tid":43241,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"批判即食文化對咖啡文化帶來嘅沖擊！","createTime":"2016-12-17T10:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T17:04:51.000Z","uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"48c096ed2c2ea5cd1a0bba095811861348485f67","tid":43241,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T10:58:28.000Z","msg":"飲 Starbucks最好係直接去店到，gel好個頭排隊<br />\n然後到你個時係銀包到拎出一張金卡，瀟灑地放係枱面，用abc tone 講「莫卡，關地」<br />\n<br />\n但係依家啲人貪求即食文化，希望買完一 pack 返去慢慢飲，就好似師奶係百佳買午餐肉咁<br />\n<br />\n見到依類人我就覺得 Starbucks終有一日會冇曬門市，冇學生妹會在係 Starbucks一邊飲一邊溫書<br />\nPatrick Cheung 部 ipad 都唔會有機會係 Starbucks出現<br />\n因為大家都買曬樽裝返去飲，毀咗呢種文化<br />\n<br />\n悲矣！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/e6j7zynq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fe6j7zynq&h=67794614&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"056d78e94cd3e6b4da1ca628df9dc0beb7b18617","tid":43241,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T10:59:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 飲咖啡嘅同時，請大家直接去店飲，唔好再買返屋企。聽到 Staff 叫杯野個名，你唔覺好興奮咩？"},{"pid":"faae6ac8d48133df9678e8c08624525d4d8e16a7","tid":43241,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T11:02:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b58040df9e3092813ffcf5967e979e1ba3d0bdc8","tid":43241,"uid":44982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T11:02:51.000Z","msg":"啱呀啱呀，飲屎打畢屎一定要門市飲咁就唔算即食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a15608e9b5e00f0d216e8ec9f3d534957e1c20","tid":43241,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T11:11:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":